Class LaunchConfigurationAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • sk.stuba.fiit.perconik.core.AbstractRegistrable
      • sk.stuba.fiit.perconik.core.Adapter
        • sk.stuba.fiit.perconik.core.adapters.LaunchConfigurationAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.eclipse.debug.core.ILaunchConfigurationListener, Listener, LaunchConfigurationListener, Registrable

    public class LaunchConfigurationAdapter
extends Adapter
implements LaunchConfigurationListener
    An abstract adapter class for a LaunchConfigurationListener. The methods in this class are empty. This class exists as convenience for creating listener objects.

    Extend this class to create a LaunchConfigurationListener and override the methods for the events of interest.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Pavol Zbell
